    </data>
  </group>
</infobox>
</includeonly>
<noinclude>
== Weapon Template ==

This template renders an infobox for weapon pages. It automatically loads data from [[Module:Weapons_data]] based on the page name.

=== Automatic Data Loading ===

When used as <code><nowiki>{{Weapon}}</nowiki></code>, the template automatically queries [[Module:Weapons_data]] using <code><nowiki>{{PAGENAME}}</nowiki></code> as the lookup key. No parameters are required on weapon pages that exist in the data module.

=== Manual Override (Backward Compatible) ===

All parameters can be manually specified to override the automatic data:

<pre>
{{Weapon
  | title1 = Example
  | image1 = Example.jpg
  | caption-image1 = Example
  | cost = Example
  | weight = Example
  | required_tech_level = Example
  | technology_required = Example
  | shield_damage = Example
  | armor_piercing = Example
  | energy_drain = Example
  | damage_radius = Example
  | accuracy = Example
  | shots_per_turn = Example
  | energy_per_shot = Example
  | max_targets_per_turn = Example
  | offensive_merit = Example
}}
</pre>

